Current entry path
boilerplate_iosApp (@main) -> AppRootView.swift -> MapView.swift

The live app entry point is boilerplate_iosApp.swift. Its WindowGroup renders AppRootView().
AppRootView.swift currently returns only MapView(), so the app launches directly into the map.
The active SwiftUI preview for this flow is also in AppRootView.swift.

Important current scope notes
The commented-out AppPreferences / shell code in boilerplate_iosApp.swift and AppRootView.swift is not part of the current MapView path.
AppShellView.swift, AccessibleAppShellView.swift, AppTab.swift, AppTabContentView.swift, and Screens.swift exist for a larger tabbed app shell, but MapView is not being entered through that shell right now.
